</li>
<li>2005 â <a href="/wiki/AFI%27s_100_Years..._100_Movie_Quotes" title="AFI's 100 Years... 100 Movie Quotes" class="mw-redirect">AFI's 100 Years... 100 Movie Quotes</a>
<ul>
<li>"Madness. Madness" â Nominated</li>
</ul>
