<li>2006 â <a href="/wiki/AFI%27s_100_Years..._100_Cheers" title="AFI's 100 Years... 100 Cheers" class="mw-redirect">AFI's 100 Years... 100 Cheers</a> â #14</li>
<li>2007 â <a href="/wiki/AFI%27s_100_Years..._100_Movies_(10th_Anniversary_Edition)" title="AFI's 100 Years... 100 Movies (10th Anniversary Edition)" class="mw-redirect">AFI's 100 Years... 100 Movies (10th Anniversary Edition)</a> â #36</li>
